name: Chevhell lovely
text:
Ordered my two pepperoni pizza on the phone and picked up my pizza in person.
The pizza was not fresh. It seemed like it they sitting in the hot box all day! The pizza was dripping grease and tasted stale! :(

name: Pierre Cervantes
text: Well made. Good service

name: Michael Wilder II
text: Pizza was hot!!! Average tasting pizza. Nothing too fancy or out of the ordinary.

name: Yolande Fong
text: Being single, a pizza lasts for 4 meals! Fantastic value!

name: Joshua Walker
text: Curbside pick up takes way too long. Never got my food. Had to go inside.

name: Tesra L.
text: Very fast service and curbside pick up was outstanding

name: R Mendoza
text: Kids were very happy with their personal fresh pizza! Busy location.

name: Cal A
text: Expensive when compared to Whole Foods and Costco.

name: December Nevels
text: The pizza was delicious and really fresh. I placed the order online and in previous experiences , other places made it way too early and then it’s cold and I no longer really want the pizza. The customer service was pretty good as well !

name: Brian Yamane
text: Pizza hut is going downhill. Used to be good a while back but haven't had a tasty one for years. Don't plan on going back anytime soon, lots of other good pizza outlets to choose from

name: Piano Man
text:
Take out only. I'm in love with their Buffalo Wings. Who knew? And I rate my Buffalo Wings like the original Anchor Bar.  Get a pack to go.
1 star off cuz they don't come with celery and blue cheese (go get that from Shoppers separately)

name: Emma Mitchell
text: I have never had a bad experience with this Pizza Hut. Their chicken alfredo is perfection.

name: Robert Harris
text: Don't order the chicken alfredo, you will be puking all night long & have the runs.

name: Madison J
text: Favorite pizza to order!

name: Jake Freeman
text: Dis location is for take out...no dining area inside, but  rt outside get dining area.

name: Maranda Roy
text: My cheese sticks were awful!! So dry! They wouldn’t even let me add extra cheese to them, even offered to pay.

name: Michael Wong
text: Love  that  pizza.

text: One Pizza

text: Good customer service and fast service
